 8 - 9 hours • Private group • Pickup available 5(32) From $354 $318 per group up to 5Image 17: image Tokyo Mt Fuji 5th St & Hakone Cruise Bus Tour w/Bullet Train 10 hours • Optional audio guide 4.4(5,201) From $152Image 18: image Top rated Tokyo：Shibuya Go Karting Tour from Shinjuku to Shibuya 1 hour • Skip the line • Small group 4.7(247) From $58Image 19: image From Tokyo: Mt. Fuji & Hakone Tour w/ Return"
